Denzabar, Running with his mates, realized he had forgotten his hammer, he'd 
have to go back for it alone. He did. Run back, the seven foot neanderthal 
took several giants steps until he reached the ship. In his ignorance, though, he 
walked up to the ship to retrieve his hammer which  was moved somehow. He 
walks up to the ship unknowing o the weapon and technology of the ship.

--part1_8f.320d7e84.2c9c440c_boundary
